Adam Smith. But according to <a href="https://www.guardianbookshop.com/enlightenment-now-549057.html" data-link-name="in body link"><em>Enlightenment Now</em></a>, a new book by the celebrated Harvard cognitive psychologist <a href="https://stevenpinker.com/" data-link-name="in body link">Steven Pinker</a>, this is precisely where we’re getting our priorities wrong.</p><div id="sign-in-gate"><gu-island name="SignInGateSelector" priority="feature" deferUntil="visible" props="{&quot;contentType&quot;:&quot;Article&quot;,&quot;sectionId&quot;:&quot;science&quot;,&quot;tags&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;science/steven-pinker&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;Keyword&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Steven Pinker&quot;},{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;books/scienceandnature&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;Keyword&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Science and nature books&quot;},{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;books/books&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;Keyword&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Books&quot;},{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;science/psychology&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;Keyword&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Psychology&quot;},{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;environment/environment&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;Keyword&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Environment&quot;},{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;society/poverty&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;Keyword&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Poverty&quot;},{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;inequality/inequality&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;Keyword&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Inequality&quot;},{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;science/science&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;Keyword&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Science&quot;},{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;culture/culture&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;Keyword&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Culture&quot;},{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;tone/features&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;Tone&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Features&quot;},{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;type/article&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;Type&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Article&quot;},{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;profile/andrewanthony&quot;